{"lang": "zh_CN", "eventid": "main_17", "eventName": "相变临界", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "EG-11", "avgTag": "幕间", "storyName": "时间之后", "storyInfo": "普瑞赛斯借凯尔希的眼睛，重新审视着这个年幼的文明。", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "60_g1_rhodescorridor_bc", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_sys_act1mainss_intro", "key": "$m_sys_act1mainss_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Dr.{@nickname}，还在挑选那些诗集吗？"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没什么，我刚才想到了一首诗，也可以放入其中。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想让我念给你听吗？"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "60_g3_cvilizationtombstone", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "倘若群星燃烧着关怀我们的激情，", "x": 300.0, "y": 230.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n我们却无法回报，我们作何感想？", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n现在我看群星，我却难以启齿，", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n说我成天思念一颗星星。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "倘若所有的星星消失或者消亡，", "x": 300.0, "y": 230.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n我应该学会仰望空荡的天空，", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n同时感受宇宙一片漆黑的崇高，", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n虽然这样可能要花费一点时间。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n......", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原来......这就是你一万年的旅程。"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我该如何重新认识你，AMa-10......"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者说......凯尔希？"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "60_g4_rhodesabyss_w", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的行为对源石计划造成了不小的阻碍，但是跟着你的视线，或许是了解如今的泰拉文明最直接的方式。"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原来如此......"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "PCS系统，保存者的维生舱，幸存的巨兽，破损的星门......那些破碎遗迹，竟然是以这种方式塑造了新生文明的样貌。"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出人意料的结果，却因过于荒唐而显得有趣。"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但最重要的是，源石改变了这些生命的样貌，也引导他们走上了与我们的文明相似的路。"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Dr.{@nickname}，从塔卫二召唤来的生命火种是你自作主张的选择，这样的结果符合你的期待吗？"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_23_G07", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到了......"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原始而远离危机的环境为生命保留了野蛮生长的空间，演化出了形态各异的文明，这是失落时代许久不曾见到的景象......"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它的确令人感动，我并非无法理解。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，难道就仅此而已？"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_cenbri", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你曾经还记得的，我们经历过多少次被寄予厚望的计划在末日中灰飞烟灭，我们的同胞为了冲破终极的黑暗前赴后继地牺牲。"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所剩不多的希望被无休止地消磨，那是极度的残忍。"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相比之下，在这颗渺小的星球上，这个还会因语言和文化产生隔阂，因为政治而爆发战争的原始文明，如何能算得上“希望”？"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不明白，到底是什么说服了你......"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "49_i22", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 40.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "27_i31", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.1, "yScaleTo": 1.1, "duration": 40.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "44_i12_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "ImageTween", 